data.text:
Sacred Heart School is a Catholic educational institution located in Oklahoma City, OK, offering a safe and nurturing environment for students. With a strong mission statement and dedicated staff, the school provides a comprehensive curriculum and religious education to foster the personal and academic growth of its students.

Sacred Heart Catholic Church, affiliated with the school, serves as a spiritual center for the community, offering sacraments and ministries to its members. With a rich history and commitment to the Catholic faith, the church provides a welcoming space for worship and community engagement.
